import Home from './Home'
import Settings from './Settings'
import PageNotFound from './PageNotFound'
import Machines from './Machines'
import Admin from './Admin'
import { FaHome } from 'react-icons/fa'
import { IoIosSettings } from 'react-icons/io'
import { GiWashingMachine } from 'react-icons/gi'
import { BiShieldQuarter } from 'react-icons/bi'

const iconStyle = {verticalAlign: 'top', paddingTop: '10%'};

const pagesList = [
    {
        name: "admin_page_name",
        icon: <BiShieldQuarter style={iconStyle}/>,
        path: "/admin",
        app: <Admin />,
        title: "admin_page_title",
        admin: true
    },
    {
        name: "home_page_name",
        icon: <FaHome style={iconStyle}/>,
        path: "/home",
        app: <Home />,
        title: "home_page_title"
    },
    {
        name: "machines_page_name",
        icon: <GiWashingMachine style={iconStyle}/>,
        path: "/machines",
        app: <Machines />,
        title: "machines_page_title"
    },
    {
        name: "settings_page_name",
        icon: <IoIosSettings style={iconStyle}/>,
        path: "/settings",
        app: <Settings />,
        title: "settings_page_title"
    },
    {
        name: "PageNotFound",
        path: "/pageNotFound",
        app: <PageNotFound />,
        hidden: true,
        title: "page_not_found_title"
    }
]

export default pagesList;
